item.title: 【Singles (lossless)】FLAC - Jessica Simpson - Love Me Tender
item.description:
Hey, I've been searching for this for 2 years and I finally got it. Wanted to share it with you all. This is a cover Jessica did for the "Lilo & Stitch: Island Favorites" Disney compilation album. It was on the first pressing of the album, but was later replaced by another song. It isn't available to stream anywhere, and up until now it was only available on YouTube in a very bad quality. Hope you like it.
